description: a(n) is the Sprague-Grundy value of the Node-Kayles game on the semi-regular graph of n linked 4-cycles with vertex set {u_1, u_2, ..., u_n, u_{n+1}, v_1, w_1, v_2, w_2, ..., v_n, w_n}. In this graph, u_1, u_2, ..., u_n, and u_{n+1} form a path, and additional edges are given by {u_i, v_i}, {v_i, w_i}, and {w_i, u_{i+1}} for all i=1,2,...,n.
